name: compose
description:
Create a new, variadic procedure that is the composition of "<callable> ...".
Aliased by <*> if only given callables.

name: bind
description:
Create a new procedure by binding "<obj> ..." as arguments to <callable>.
Aliased by <+> if only given callables.

name: id
description: Returns <obj>. Useful for certain higher-level procedures.

name: procedure?
description:
Returns whether <obj> is a procedure.
Prefer <callable?> for more generic code.

name: callable?
description:
Returns whether <obj> is applicable. Equivalent to:
  (or (procedure? <obj>) (functor? <obj>) (class? <obj>))
